\begin_layout Standard
We note that the use of the Langevin equation
\begin_inset space ~
\end_inset

(
\begin_inset CommandInset ref
LatexCommand ref
reference "eq:Langevin FD"

\end_inset

) is justified only with finite values 
\begin_inset Formula $\Delta t\sim H^{-1}$
\end_inset

