\end_layout

\end_inset

 
\begin_inset Formula $P_{V}(\phi,t)d\phi$
\end_inset

, which is defined as the physical
\begin_inset Index idx
status collapsed

\begin_layout Plain Layout
physical volume
\end_layout

\end_inset

 3-volume (computed as 
\begin_inset Formula $\int\sqrt{-^{(3)}g}\,d^{3}\mathbf{x}$
\end_inset

, as opposed to the comoving volume) of regions having the value 
\begin_inset Formula $\phi$
