\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{equation}
P_{V}(\phi,t)\equiv\int_{0}^{\infty}da\,a^{3}P(\phi,a,t),
\end{equation}

\end_inset

which weighs the distribution of 
\begin_inset Formula $\phi$
\end_inset

