\begin_inset space ~
\end_inset

(
\begin_inset CommandInset ref
LatexCommand ref
reference "eq:FP V"

\end_inset

).
 This establishes a link between the volume interpretation of the distribution
 
\begin_inset Formula $P_{V}(\phi,t)$
\end_inset

