However, as is well known, the WKB approximation produces only an asymptotic
 series whose precision is fundamentally limited.
 An estimate of the best possible precision of the WKB approximation can
 be found in 
\begin_inset CommandInset citation
LatexCommand cite
key "Winitzki:2005rw"
literal "true"

\end_inset

.
\end_layout

\end_inset

 
\end_layout

\begin_layout Section
Presence of eternal inflation
\begin_inset CommandInset label
LatexCommand label
name "sec:Presence-of-eternal"

\end_inset


\begin_inset CommandInset label
