key "Vilenkin:1998kr"
literal "true"

\end_inset

.
 This prescription provides unambiguous predictions for models of random-walk
 type eternal inflation if the reheating condition 
\begin_inset Formula $\phi=\phi_{*}$
\end_inset

 corresponds to a topologically compact and connected locus in the field
 space 
\begin_inset Formula $\left\{ \phi,\chi_{a}\right\} $
\end_inset

 (see Sec.
\begin_inset space ~
\end_inset


\begin_inset CommandInset ref
