reference "subsec:Predictions-in-continuous"

\end_inset

).
 For models where the reheating condition is met at several disconnected
 loci in field space (tunneling-type eternal inflation belongs to this class),
 one can use the recently proposed prescription of 
\begin_inset Quotes eld
\end_inset

comoving cutoff
