\begin_inset Formula $j$
\end_inset

.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
In scenarios of tunneling type, such as the string theory landscape, observers
 may find themselves in bubbles of types 
\begin_inset Formula $\alpha=1,...,N$
\end_inset

.
