 For clarity, we illustrate these weighting prescriptions on models of tunneling
 type where infinitely many nested bubbles of types 
\begin_inset Formula $\alpha=1,...N$
\end_inset

 are created and where some bubbles are 
\begin_inset Quotes eld
\end_inset

terminal,
\begin_inset Quotes erd
\end_inset

 
\emph on
i.e.
\emph default

\begin_inset space ~
\end_inset

can contain no 
\begin_inset Quotes eld
\end_inset

daughter
\begin_inset Quotes erd
\end_inset

