 Instead it focuses only on the reheated 3-volume of one 
\begin_inset Formula $H$
\end_inset

-region surrounding a 
\emph on
single
\emph default
 randomly chosen comoving worldline.
 This measure, by construction, is sensitive to the initial conditions at
