\begin_inset Formula $g(z_{*};\phi)$
\end_inset

 to the approximations
\begin_inset space ~
\end_inset

(
\begin_inset CommandInset ref
LatexCommand ref
reference "eq:g approx 2"

\end_inset

) and (
\begin_inset CommandInset ref
LatexCommand ref
reference "eq:g approx 1"

\end_inset

) at some intermediate points straddling 
\begin_inset Formula $\phi=\phi_{0}$
\end_inset

.
