 However, the accuracy of the approximations
\begin_inset space ~
\end_inset

(
\begin_inset CommandInset ref
LatexCommand ref
reference "eq:g approx 2"

\end_inset

) and (
\begin_inset CommandInset ref
LatexCommand ref
reference "eq:g approx 1"

\end_inset

