\begin_inset CommandInset ref
LatexCommand ref
reference "subsec:FPRV-distribution-of-Q"

\end_inset

, is to compute the eigenfunction 
\begin_inset Formula $f_{0}(z_{*};\phi)$
\end_inset

 of the operator 
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{equation}
\hat{\tilde{L}}\equiv\frac{D_{0}}{H_{0}}\partial_{\phi}\partial_{\phi}+3(\ln g(z_{*};\phi)+1)
\end{equation}

\end_inset

such that
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{equation}
\hat{\tilde{L}}f_{0}=0;\quad f_{0}(z_{*};\phi_{1,2})=0.
