\end_inset

-bubbles to 
\begin_inset Formula $B$
\end_inset

-bubbles,
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{equation}
\frac{p(A)}{p(B)}=\frac{z_{*}\kappa_{FA}\kappa_{IF}}{\left(\frac{1}{\nu}F_{*}^{\frac{1}{\nu}-1}-\kappa_{FF}\right)\kappa_{IB}},\label{eq:AB ratio}
