LatexCommand ref
reference "eq:F equ 2"

\end_inset

).
 This is equivalent to assuming 
\begin_inset Formula $\eta\ll\nu^{-2}$
\end_inset

.
 In the range of 
\begin_inset Formula $z$
\end_inset

 for which this is the case, 
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{equation}
z\kappa_{FI}I(z)\ll z\kappa_{FA}\ll1;\quad z\kappa_{IB}\ll z\kappa_{IF}F(z)\ll1,\label{eq:regime 2}
