\frac{\kappa_{IB}}{\kappa_{IF}\kappa_{FA}^{\nu}}\ll z^{\nu}\ll\left[\kappa_{FA}^{\nu^{2}-1}\kappa_{FI}\kappa_{IF}^{\nu}\right]^{-\frac{1}{\nu+1}}.\label{eq:regime 2 cond}
