\end_inset

 satisfy 
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{equation}
\hat{M}(z)\left[\begin{array}{c}
F_{,r}\\
I_{,r}
\end{array}\right]=\left[\begin{array}{c}
\kappa_{FF}F\\
z\kappa_{IF}F
