\end_inset

Using the same arguments as in the previous section, we evaluate the limit
 of Eq.
\begin_inset space ~
\end_inset

(
\begin_inset CommandInset ref
LatexCommand ref
reference "eq:BB pre ans 1"

\end_inset

),
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{equation}
\lim_{n\rightarrow\infty}\left.\frac{\partial_{z}^{n}\partial_{r}I}{\partial_{z}^{n}\partial_{q}I}\right|_{z=0,r=1,q=1}=\nu F_{*}^{1-\frac{1}{\nu}}\kappa_{FF}+1.\label{eq:BB ans 1}
\end{equation}

\end_inset

To analyze this simple result, we do not actually need to use the complicated
 decision procedure of Sec.
\begin_inset space ~
\end_inset


\begin_inset CommandInset ref
LatexCommand ref
reference "subsec:A-toy-landscape"

