 of transitions with nonzero nucleation rates.
 This condition has been discussed in 
\begin_inset CommandInset citation
LatexCommand cite
key "Garriga:2005av,Garriga:2008ks"
literal "true"

\end_inset

.
 Note that a nonzero transition probability from vacuum 
\begin_inset Formula $i$
\end_inset

 to vacuum 
\begin_inset Formula $j$
\end_inset

 (where both 
\begin_inset Formula $i$
\end_inset

 and 
\begin_inset Formula $j$
\end_inset

