\begin_inset space ~
\end_inset

(
\begin_inset CommandInset ref
LatexCommand ref
reference "eq:main branch landscape"

\end_inset

) shows that 
\begin_inset Formula $g(z;i)>0$
\end_inset

 for sufficiently small 
\begin_inset Formula $z>0$
\end_inset

, and it follows that 
\begin_inset Formula $g(z;i)$
\end_inset

 will remain positive for all 
\begin_inset Formula $z>0$
\end_inset

 such that 
\begin_inset Formula $\lambda_{0}(z)>0$
\end_inset

.
