\begin_inset Formula $g(z;i)$
\end_inset

, 
\begin_inset Formula $i=1$
\end_inset

, ..., 
\begin_inset Formula $N_{r}$
\end_inset

 are strictly increasing functions of 
\begin_inset Formula $z$
\end_inset

 for all those 
\begin_inset Formula $z$
\end_inset

.
