\end{equation}

\end_inset

In other words, no real-valued solutions of Eq.
\begin_inset space ~
\end_inset

(
\begin_inset CommandInset ref
LatexCommand ref
reference "eq:g equ for q1"

\end_inset

) exist for larger 
\begin_inset Formula $z$
\end_inset

.
 Let us then show that an upper bound on 
\begin_inset Formula $z$
\end_inset

 contradicts the assumption that 
\begin_inset Formula $\lambda_{0}(z)>0$
\end_inset

 for all 
\begin_inset Formula $z$
\end_inset

.
