\end{equation}

\end_inset

hence
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{equation}
\frac{d\lambda_{0}(z)}{dz}=-\frac{\lambda_{0}(z)}{z_{*}-z}+O(z_{*}-z).
\end{equation}

\end_inset

We then use Eq.
\begin_inset space ~
\end_inset

(
\begin_inset CommandInset ref
LatexCommand ref
reference "eq:dlambda dz"

\end_inset

) to express 
\begin_inset Formula $d\lambda_{0}/dz$
\end_inset

