= & \left\langle u^{0}(z)\right|\left[\sum_{i}\frac{\partial\hat{M}}{\partial g(z;i)}\partial_{z}g(z;i)+\partial_{z}\hat{M}(z)\right]\left|v^{0}(z)\right\rangle ,
\end{align}

\end_inset

where in the second line we interpreted 
\begin_inset Formula $\hat{M}(z)$
\end_inset

 as a function of 
\begin_inset Formula $N_{r}$
\end_inset

 variables 
\begin_inset Formula $g(z;i)$
\end_inset

, 
\begin_inset Formula $i=1,...,N_{r}$
\end_inset

, and explicitly of 
\begin_inset Formula $z$
\end_inset

, in order to express 
\begin_inset Formula $d/dz$
\end_inset

 through 
\begin_inset Formula $\partial/\partial g$
\end_inset

 and 
\begin_inset Formula $\partial/\partial z$
\end_inset

.
